text: Wesley Koolhof and Matwé Middelkoop were the defending champions but chose not to participate. Sanchai and Sonchat Ratiwatana won the title after defeating Sadio Doumbia and Fabien Reboul 7–6(7–4), 7–5 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw 2017 Bangkok II Challenger - Doubles Category:Bangkok Challenger II
